---
---

<section class="about rx">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text rxl">
        <span class="about-eyebrow">About Hughey LLC</span>
        <h2 class="about-title">20 Years. One Industry.</h2>
        <p>We've spent two decades focused exclusively on law firm marketing. Not restaurant marketing, not SaaS marketing, not e-commerce. Law firms. That focus is the entire difference.</p>
        <p>We understand your business because we've helped hundreds of firms navigate the shift from lead volume to lead quality, from vanity metrics to retained client ROI, from reactive vendor management to strategic planning.</p>
        <p>Most of our work isn't flashy. It's unglamorous: untangling messy data, rebuilding intake workflows, auditing vendors, training teams. But it works.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="about-cta">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-bio rxr">
        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-avatar">JH</div>
          <div class="bio-name">Joe Hughey</div>
          <div class="bio-title">Founder</div>
          <div class="bio-stats">
            <div class="bio-stat">
              <div class="bio-stat-num">150+</div>
              <div class="bio-stat-label">Firms Guided</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bio-stat">
              <div class="bio-stat-num">20+</div>
              <div class="bio-stat-label">Years in Legal</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="bio-text">Joe spent two decades learning how law firms actually grow. Not from textbooks or MBA case studies — from working directly with managing partners, operations teams, and marketers. That experience is the foundation for everything we do.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FAFAF5 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(380px, 1fr));
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--sub);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .about-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-cta:hover {
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--glt);
  }

  .bio-card {
    padding: 40px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bio-avatar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--glt));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--bar);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }

  .bio-name {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .bio-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .bio-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .bio-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--bar);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .bio-stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--sub);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--sub);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
